            "policy_content": "<p><strong>Website:</strong> sundaze.com<br/><strong>Contact:</strong> support@sundaze.com</p><p>Thank you for shopping with Sundaze. Because our products are age-restricted hemp-derived goods, all sales are final.</p><h2>1. No Refunds</h2><p>All purchases from Sundaze are final.</p><p>We do not offer refunds, returns, or exchanges once an order is placed, except where required by law or approved by Sundaze in its sole discretion.</p><p>By placing an order, you acknowledge and agree that:</p><ul><li>Products cannot be returned for a refund.</li><li>Opened products cannot be returned.</li><li>Used products cannot be returned.</li><li>Refused packages are not eligible for a refund.</li><li>Orders shipped to an incorrect address entered by the customer are not eligible for a refund.</li><li>Shipping fees are non-refundable.</li><li>Route/package protection fees, if offered, are non-refundable.</li></ul><h2>2. Order Cancellations</h2><p>Orders may not be canceled once processing has started.</p><p>If you need to request a cancellation, contact us immediately at <strong>support@sundaze.com</strong>. We may approve or deny cancellation requests depending on fulfillment status.</p><p>Sundaze reserves the right to cancel any order for compliance, payment, fraud, inventory, restricted-shipping, or legal reasons.</p><h2>3. Damaged, Missing, or Incorrect Items</h2><p>If your order arrives damaged, missing an item, or contains the wrong item, contact us within <strong>48 hours of delivery</strong> at <strong>support@sundaze.com</strong>.</p><p>Please include:</p><ul><li>Order number</li><li>Full name</li><li>Delivery address</li><li>Photos of the package</li><li>Photos of the damaged or incorrect item</li><li>Photos of the packing slip, if available</li></ul><p>Approved claims may be resolved through a replacement, store credit, or another remedy selected by Sundaze.</p><p>Refunds are not guaranteed.</p><h2>4. Lost or Stolen Packages</h2><p>Sundaze is not responsible for packages marked as delivered by the shipping carrier.</p><p>If your package is marked as delivered but cannot be located, please:</p><ul><li>Check with household members</li><li>Check around the delivery area</li><li>Contact the shipping carrier</li><li>Contact us at <strong>support@sundaze.com</strong> with your order number</li></ul><p>We may assist with carrier information, but replacement or store credit is not guaranteed.</p><h2>5. Failed Delivery or Incorrect Address</h2><p>Customers are responsible for providing complete and accurate shipping information.</p><p>Sundaze is not responsible for:</p><ul><li>Incorrect addresses</li><li>Missing apartment or unit numbers</li><li>Failed delivery attempts</li><li>Refused packages</li><li>Packages returned due to customer error</li><li>Packages delayed or rejected because of age verification or shipping restrictions</li></ul><p>Orders returned to sender are not automatically eligible for a refund.</p><h2>6. Chargebacks</h2><p>If there is an issue with your order, please contact us before filing a chargeback.</p><p>We actively investigate and dispute fraudulent or improper chargebacks.</p><h2>7. Contact</h2><p>For order issues, please contact:</p><p><strong>Sundaze Support</strong><br/><strong>Email:</strong> support@sundaze.com</p>"
